title: I cant use Annie in wonderland
body: I cant use Annie in wonder land I know I have it. I got a mystery gift from a friend. I can no longer use it because it appears i don't own it.

replies.body: We've had some previous issues with certain skins displaying in your summoner profile, but will still display in champ select. Can you confirm whether or not this skin is showing up in champ select?
Then I'd recommend reaching out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can take a look at what happened and provide you context.
